#: sentifyd-avatar.php:348
msgid ""
"This plugin embeds the Sentifyd avatar web component which stores session-scoped data in the browser (sessionStorage) to "
"maintain UI state and conversation context. Keys may include avatar open/closed state, authentication data such as short-"
"lived tokens, and conversation transcript. Data clears when the tab/window closes. No data is stored in cookies or local "
"storage by the widget."
msgstr ""

