#: sentifyd-avatar.php:436
msgid ""
"Optional. If provided, the avatar will call your secure token endpoint to obtain short-lived session tokens. If omitted, "
"this plugin uses its built-in WordPress REST endpoint to mint tokens using your stored API key (which is never exposed to "
"the browser)."
msgstr ""

